::
::   get a list of plain text by preorder traversal
::
++  pre-get-text
  ^-  wall
  %-  flop
  %-  pre-fold
  |=  [g=marx l=wall]
  ?.  ?=(%$ n.g)      l
  ?~  a.g             l
  ?.  ?=(%$ n.i.a.g)  l
  ?^  t.a.g           l
  :-  v.i.a.g         l
