::
::   get a list of plain text by level order traversal
::
++  lvl-get-text
  ^-  wall
  %-  flop
  %-  lvl-fold
  |=  [g=marx l=wall]
  ?.  ?=(%$ n.g)      l
  ?~  a.g             l
  ?.  ?=(%$ n.i.a.g)  l
  ?^  t.a.g           l
