:: search-text
::
:: find plain text containing the given cord
::
++  search-text
  |=  b=@t
  ^-  wall
  %-  flop
  %-  post-fold
  |=  [g=marx l=wall]
  ?.  ?=(%$ n.g)      l
  ?~  a.g             l
  ?.  ?=(%$ n.i.a.g)  l
  ?^  t.a.g           l
  =+  par=(cury (jest b) *hair)
  ?.  |-
      ?~  v.i.a.g  %.n
      ?^  (tail (par v.i.a.g))
        %.y
      $(v.i.a.g t.v.i.a.g)
    l
  [v.i.a.g l]
